original_title: Ninni Luhtasaari: A Day in the Mouth episode 11
overview: Ninni Luhtasaari is a primitive entertainer in music and visual arts. Luhtasaari is known from bands such as Ninni Forever Band, Maria ja Marsialaiset, Risto and Jari Raaste.
title: Ninni Luhtasaari: A Day in the Mouth episode 11
